## Troubleshooting

**"Generated image doesn't match brand"**:
- Check that visual-style.md base prompt is correct
- Verify Nanobanana API is using correct model
- Regenerate with more specific subject description

**"API fails"**:
- Verify NANOBANANA_API_KEY environment variable is set
- Check API quotas/billing
- See scripts/generate_image.py error logs

**"Wrong dimensions"**:
- Specify explicit --dimensions parameter
- Default is 1024x1024 (square)

**"Want to change aesthetic"**:
- Do NOT edit this skill directly
- Re-run visual-identity meta-skill to regenerate with new aesthetic
- This skill will be regenerated with updated guidelines
